{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2e4cb9fbc9","title":"毛泽东视察四川省一个养猪场的谈话(纪要)","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d39dc5b2e9","index":0,"year":1958,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"450cf61678","type":"title","text":"毛泽东视察四川省一个养猪场的谈话(纪要)","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"e9f2833f65","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"163d457ede","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：(对饲养员)辛苦了，好同志！(握手)，祝你们获得更大的成功!","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"1bb32674aa","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：全靠你老人家的教导!","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"cbd6d89f4e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：主要是你们自己的努力。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"ebe5e0165d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：(对社长)能使你们全社妇女，都当上模范吗?","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"48ab74405c","type":"paragraph","text":"社长：保证全能当上，毛主席！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"336a9cc7e0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：全当上模范未必行吧！只要在两三年内做到有一半妇女当上模范就不错了。你说我这个看法保守吗?(众笑)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"fbe3155065","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：参观一下你们的养猪场好吗?","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"ca9f1a8bab","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：欢迎，欢迎!请毛主席多多指教！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"121b1f38d3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：别什么都要我指教吧，我和××都是来向你们学习的，在许多事情上你们比我们内行多了，是吧?","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"abaf940e86","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"6076d50dfb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这是什么?","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"03268ef7ef","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：是糖化牛粪。拿来喂猪的，猪很爱吃。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"0f4452c7bd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：真是新鲜事儿，牛粪也能喂猪！怎么个制法，介绍一下好吗?(摸出笔记本来作记录，向××说)来，我们都记下吧，这是群众的创造！从前我们就没有听见说过。看来我们中国那句老话：“活到老，学到老”实在不错!","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"52acb686d9","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"4f4db90816","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：(对一个回乡知识青年)回家喂猪有意见吗?","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"63ff93a856","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：有啥意见呀！我一辈子也不愿离开这养猪场哩!","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"3402c9018e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：很好！可要把你学的科学，传授给群众才好！","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"0be7b33d99","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"9e9dfa8fbb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：……多看看先进的东西，眼光就会更开阔些。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"bb378b8670","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：(亲自给一头猪打了蛋清针，然后对××说，)这里的经验真不少，特别是代饲料，如果全国都推广，一年要节约好几十亿斤粮食哩！请记者同志在报纸上介绍一下好吗?(×××：办得到。)最好后天见报。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"090f7fcd73","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：(对饲养员)谢谢你们!对我们的教育太大了！","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"efc3b11256","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：可有人看不起我们呢!","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"f3f9dfd9ff","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：谁？谁是顽固派？(饲养员介绍一些人如何从轻视妇女到称赞妇女的成绩，)","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"},{"id":"33b0f4cc31","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：看不起妇女的人，虽不多，但哪里总有几个，这不完全怪他们，过去封建制度对他们的影响太深了，脑筋一下不容易转过来，又不能用飞机大炮来对付他们。那怎么办呢？我看除了加强教育外，最好的办法，就是妇女同志做出成绩来，多拿事实给他们看，看得多了，他们脑子里的那个封建王国就会不攻自破的!","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9"}],"page":{"id":"46e771c0d0","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2e4cb9fbc9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}